Package generator

This package contains all interfaces, abstract classes and classes that generate numbers according to certain parameters given. Any generator like this can implement GenerateNumber to be later used.

The generated numbers can be deterministic or random, and for the latter can follow different random distributions.

Generators already implemented are UnifRandom and ExpRandom.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GenerateNumber
    This interface provides the service of generating a number according to any given parameters.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExpRandom
    This class extends GenerateRandom, implementing number generator according to exponential distribution.
    GenerateRandom
    This abstract class implements the interface, adding a static Random field to be inherited by subclasses.
    UnifRandom
    This class extends GenerateRandom, implementing number generator according to uniform distribution.
